snippet.title: The ROAD To SUCCESS and The CNBC Show "The Profit" With Amber Mazzola
snippet.description:
If you think the road to success is simple for some people, and they just became successful overnight. You couldn't be further from the truth. In most cases it was a long road of hard work. Amber Mazzola shares her story of how she started her own production company and is currently the producer of the hit show "The Profit".


Audio Podcast - https://brandcreators.com/840


📒 Show Notes and Resources
